2026-04-13T05:14:05.636Z JOY-00CF-5E comment.added "Plan: 1) Add Docs struct to Project schema with optional architecture/vision/contributing path overrides. 2) Extend joy project get/set with docs.{architecture,vision,contributing} keys, returning configured value or default. 3) Rewrite check_docs in joy ai init to scan candidate paths (ARCHITECTURE.md, docs/architecture.md, docs/architecture/README.md, docs/dev/architecture/README.md, etc.), suggest first match, allow custom input, persist choice in project.yaml. 4) Add InitArgs with --architecture/--vision/--contributing flags (clap ValueHint::FilePath for shell completion). 5) Update instructions.md and SKILL.md so AI reads paths via joy project get docs.<key> and offers to fill missing/template-only docs. 6) Tests for candidate scan, default resolution, flag mode." [ai:claude@joy delegated-by:horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
