2026-04-13T05:25:23.204Z JOY-00CF-5E comment.added "[x] Added Docs struct in joy-core (architecture/vision/contributing optional fields, _or_default helpers, DEFAULT_* constants).\n[x] Extended joy project get/set with docs.architecture, docs.vision, docs.contributing keys (get returns configured value or default; set accepts empty/'none'/'default' to reset).\n[x] Rewrote check_docs in joy ai init: scans candidates per spec (e.g. for architecture: docs/dev/architecture/README.md, docs/architecture/README.md, docs/architecture.md, ARCHITECTURE.md), prompts with suggestion, persists non-default choice to project.yaml.\n[x] Added --architecture/--vision/--contributing flags on joy ai init with clap ValueHint::FilePath for shell completion.\n[x] Updated templates/ai/instructions.md and templates/ai/skills/joy/SKILL.md to read paths via 'joy project get docs.<key>' and offer to fill in missing or template-only docs.\n[x] Tests: 5 new Docs tests in joy-core (defaults, configured value, YAML round-trip, skip-when-empty), 7 new ai tests in joy-cli (resolve_doc_path precedence, suggestion scan order). All 243 tests pass; clippy clean." [ai:claude@joy delegated-by:horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
